                    <p class="pl-4 border-left border-primary">Welcome to our innovative platform, where the world of beauty and wellness meets social connectivity. We provide a unique space for users to share their beauty insights, spa experiences, and aesthetic journeys. With individual profiles tailored to each user, discovering new trends has never been easier. Seamlessly integrated appointment scheduling ensures a hassle-free experience, allowing users to book their desired procedures at renowned studios directly through the app. Join our vibrant community today and embark on a transformative voyage towards self-care and rejuvenation.</p>
                    <div class="row pt-3">
                        <div class="col-6">
                            <div class="bg-light text-center p-4">
                                <h3 class="display-4 text-primary" data-toggle="counter-up">@Model.UsersCount</h3>
                                <h6 class="text-uppercase">Happy Users</h6>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-6">
                            <div class="bg-light text-center p-4">
                                <h3 class="display-4 text-primary" data-toggle="counter-up">@Model.StudiosCount</h3>
